trans-unit.source: Specifies the number of service instances available for handling calls that are contained in incoming messages.
trans-unit.target: Angir hvor mange forekomster tilgjengelig for behandling av anrop som finnes i innkommende meldinger.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext?displayProperty=fullName> manages the association between the channel and the user-defined service objects.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext?displayProperty=fullName>administrerer tilknytning mellom kanalen og brukerdefinerte serviceobjekter.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the InstanceContextMode enumeration with the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to specify the lifetime of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object.
trans-unit.target: Bruk InstanceContextMode opplistingen med den <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>til å angi levetiden for den <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objektet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] can create a new <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object for every call, every session or specify that the <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object is bound to a single service object.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]kan opprette en ny <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objekt for hvert kall, hver økten, eller angi at den <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objektet er bundet til en enkelt Webtjenesteobjektet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> </xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: For a working example, see the [Instancing](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For eksempel en fungerer, kan du se den [Instancing](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The Single value specifies that a single <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object should be used for the lifetime of the service.
trans-unit.target: Enkeltverdien angir at én <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objektet som skal brukes for levetiden for tjenesten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > If the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A> value is set to Single the result is that your service can only process one message at a time unless you also set the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.ConcurrencyMode%2A> value to <xref:System.ServiceModel.ConcurrencyMode>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Hvis <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A>verdien er satt til én resultatet er at tjenesten kan bare behandle en melding om gangen med mindre du også angi <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.ConcurrencyMode%2A>verdien til <xref:System.ServiceModel.ConcurrencyMode>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ConcurrencyMode> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.ConcurrencyMode%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: A new <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object is created prior to and recycled subsequent to each call.
trans-unit.target: En ny <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objektet er opprettet før og resirkulert etter hvert kall.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: If the channel does not create a session this value behaves as if it were PerCall.
trans-unit.target: Hvis kanalen ikke opprette en økt fungere denne verdien som om den var PerCall.

trans-unit.source: A new <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object is created for each session.
trans-unit.target: En ny <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objekt er opprettet for hver økt.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: Only one <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object is used for all incoming calls and is not recycled subsequent to the calls.
trans-unit.target: Bare én <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objektet brukes for alle innkommende samtaler og er ikke resirkulert etter kall.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: If a service object does not exist, one is created.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en tjenesteobjektet ikke finnes, opprettes en.
